{
  "texts": [
    "By sorting out the foundational theory, researchers will be able to more clearly understand the essence and purpose of graph pooling.",
    "Section 3 will focus on the frontier research on graph pooling.",
    "We will sort out the latest progress in the field of graph pooling in recent years, including the most representative methods, algorithm optimization, and performance improvement research results.",
    "By comparing and analyzing the advantages and disadvantages of different methods, we will provide researchers with a comprehensive and in-depth perspective.",
    "The representative datasets and computational frameworks for graph pooling methods will be presented in Sects."
